<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='305021' id='t-305021'>I began to sing, and not quietly either.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='307313' id='t-307313'>'Come to the Florida sunshine bush.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='310417' id='t-310417'>Do you want to dance?'</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='311728' id='t-311728'>'Are you on drugs?' one asked. 'Are you high?'</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='314203' id='t-314203'>'High? Me? No way, no drugs.</span>
