<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322499' id='t-322499'>'You're frightening me,' one of them said, and Rebel and Val</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='325193' id='t-325193'>headed back into the library.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='326972' id='t-326972'>I shrugged and followed them.</span>
