<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='503084' id='t-503084'>We don't like to be strapped down to a bed</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='505442' id='t-505442'>and left to suffer for hours any more than he would.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='507772' id='t-507772'>In fact, until very recently,</span>
