<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590180' id='t-590180'>I refused to take more medication.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='592193' id='t-592193'>The mission is not yet complete.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='594993' id='t-594993'>Immediately after the appointment with Kaplan,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597611' id='t-597611'>I went to see Dr. Marder, a schizophrenia expert</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='599909' id='t-599909'>who was following me for medication side effects.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='602217' id='t-602217'>He was under the impression that I had a mild psychotic illness.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='605238' id='t-605238'>Once in his office, I sat on his couch, folded over,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='608666' id='t-608666'>and began muttering.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='610305' id='t-610305'>'Head explosions and people trying to kill.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='612535' id='t-612535'>Is it okay if I totally trash your office?'</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='615000' id='t-615000'>'You need to leave if you think you're going to do that,'</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='617632' id='t-617632'>said Marder.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='618615' id='t-618615'>'Okay. Small. Fire on ice. Tell them not to kill me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='621767' id='t-621767'>Tell them not to kill me. What have I done wrong?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='623415' id='t-623415'>Hundreds of thousands with thoughts, interdiction.'</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='625992' id='t-625992'>'Elyn, do you feel like you're</span>
