</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='676219' id='t-676219'>Everything about this illness says I shouldn't be here,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='678892' id='t-678892'>but I am. And I am, I think, for three reasons:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='681766' id='t-681766'>First, I've had excellent treatment.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684158' id='t-684158'>Four- to five-day-a-week psychoanalytic psychotherapy</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='687104' id='t-687104'>for decades and continuing, and excellent psychopharmacology.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690088' id='t-690088'>Second, I have many close family members and friends who know me</span>
