<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='701845' id='t-701845'>Third, I work at an enormously supportive workplace</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705013' id='t-705013'>at USC Law School.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706598' id='t-706598'>This is a place that not only accommodates my needs</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='709623' id='t-709623'>but actually embraces them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='711014' id='t-711014'>It's also a very intellectually stimulating place,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='714045' id='t-714045'>and occupying my mind with complex problems</span>
